Description:
Canonicalize a host name: return a name other hosts can understand, i.e.
usually the host name including FQDN.

Files:
lib/canon-host.c
lib/canon-host.h
m4/canon-host.m4

Depends-on:
getaddrinfo
strdup

configure.ac:
gl_CANON_HOST

Makefile.am:

Include:
#include "canon-host.h"

